name: Man #1
line: All right, folks, if you could please take your seats, we're about to enter the wormhole.

name: Rick
line: Those aren't the questions you should be asking.

name: Man #1
line: All right, folks, you're free to get up and walk around the cabin and maybe take the wormhole out for breakfast.

name: Man #2
line: Okay, you can do the dinner one or the breakfast one, but not both.
